HMV Is In Talks to Sell Its Stake In Music Service 7digital, Sky News Says

-- B y   K a r e n   E e u w e n s
-- 
2011-10-16T10:28:01Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-16/hmv-negotiating-to-sell-music-service-7digital-stake-sky-says.html
HMV Group Plc (HMV)  is in talks to sell
its stake in music service 7digital,  Sky News   reported , citing
people close to the company it didn’t name.  The U.K. retailer is in talks with several prospective
buyers, which are thought to be technology companies, Sky said.
A deal is still “some way off,” according to the news service.  HMV may choose to reduce its shareholding in 7digital
without selling the asset entirely, Sky said, citing the
unidentified people close to the company.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Karen Eeuwens in London 
 keeuwens@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Francisco Marcelino at 
 mdeoliveira@bloomberg.net . 